OL,3,CMark Drakeford launches attack on
OL,4,CLabour colleague over school holiday
OL,5,Cdecision
OL,7,FFormer First Minister Mark Drakeford
OL,8,Fmade a stinging intervention in the
OL,9,FSenedd following the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment's announcement to scrap its
OL,11,Fplans to shake-up the school calendar.
OL,13,FThe ex-first minister criticised the
OL,14,FWelsh Government's decision not to
OL,15,Fpush ahead and reform the school year
OL,16,Fby cutting the six-week holidays to
OL,17,Ffive, and extending the autumn half
OL,18,Fterm to two weeks.
