OL,7,FDrakeford was speaking in the Senedd
OL,8,Fwhen he slammed the Education
OL,9,FSecretary's decision to row back on
OL,10,Fplans to shorten school summer
OL,11,Fholidays.
OL,13,FA Labour source told ITV Cymru Wales
OL,14,Fthey had never seen anything like it
OL,15,Fbefore.
OL,17,FMr Drakeford said: "What we've heard
OL,18,Fthis afternoon is the abandonment of a
OL,19,Fmanifesto commitment."
