OL,7,FMs Neagle was deputy mental health
OL,8,Fminister in Mr Drakeford's cabinet.
OL,10,FThe exchange comes a day before First
OL,11,FMinister Vaughan Gething, Mr
OL,12,FDrakeford's successor, faces a
OL,13,FConservative-tabled confidence vote in
OL,14,Fthe Senedd.
OL,16,FPlans to cut the school summer
OL,17,Fholidays in Wales were shelved until
OL,18,Fafter the next Welsh Parliament
OL,19,Felection in 2026.
