OL,7,FIt followed a mixed response from the
OL,8,Fbiggest Welsh Government education
OL,9,Fconsultation on record, which
OL,10,Fgenerated more than 16,000 responses
OL,11,Fand sought views on changing the
OL,12,Fschool calendar to spread school
OL,13,Fholidays out more evenly across the
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FIf the proposals had gone ahead, the
OL,17,Fhalf term break in October 2025 would
OL,18,Fhave been extended to a fortnight,
OL,19,Fwith a five-week rather than six-week
OL,20,Fholiday in summer 2026.
