OL,8,Funtil the next Senedd term would allow
OL,9,Fschools to focus on other major
OL,10,Fimprovements.
OL,12,FWelsh Conservatives' shadow education
OL,13,Fminister Tom Giffard MS said: "It
OL,14,Fappears that under the strain of the
OL,15,Fupcoming vote of no confidence in the
OL,16,Ffirst minister, Labour is struggling
OL,17,Fto keep it together.
